description: Vehicle Testing and Regular Driving dashboard.

targets.query:
from(bucket: "CAN_log")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "MC")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["class"] == "Mitsuba_Frame1")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "DriveActionStatus")
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1ms, fn: last, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "last")
